Are you sure you don&#39;t mean 1.14.1? (Heritrix 1.4 was released in April 
2005.)

Heritrix 1.x has some mechanisms to try to limit the creation of URIs to 
only supported URI-schemes, so you might be running into that. Check all 
the logs (especially uri-errors.log) for evidence your URIs might be 
discarded as illegal, and take a look in the source code at the 
UURIFactory &#39;schemes&#39; and &#39;ignoredSchemes&#39; fields, and how they may be 
initialized from properties, for a place you may need to add your new 
scheme.

- Gordon @ IA

